data.description: First time home buyer or investment opportunity. 3 bedroom 2 full bath home. Very clean! Large den, wood burning fireplace with matching built in lighted bookcase. No carpet in this home, Tile and plank flooring. Tray ceiling in large primary bedroom. Primary bath has soaking tub and walk in shower. Kitchen has lots of cabinets for storage. Refrigerator to remain with home. Newly installed, Laminate wood flooring, range/oven and architectural shingle roof. Flood zone "C".  (flooring for closets not installed but flooring material remains for installation by new owner)
